{"word":"Solomon","slug":"solomon","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Solomon</b> <a href=\"#/H8010\">H8010</a><br/><a href=\"#/G4672\">G4672</a> <br/> Son of David by Bath-Sheba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=24'>2Sa 12:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=13'>1Ki 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=17'>1Ki 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=21'>1Ki 1:21</a><br/> Named Jedidiah, by Nathan the prophet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=25'>2Sa 12:25</a><br/> Ancestor of Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=6'>Mat 1:6</a><br/> Succeeds David to the throne of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=48'>1Ki 1:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=12'>1Ki 2:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=1'>1Ch 23:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=28'>1Ch 28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=1&verse=12'>Ecc 1:12</a><br/> Anointed king a second time<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=22'>1Ch 29:22</a><br/> His prayer for wisdom, and his vision<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=14'>1Ki 3:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Ch 1:12</a><br/> Covenant renewed in a vision after the dedication of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=9'>1Ki 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=7&verse=22'>2Ch 7:22</a><br/> His rigorous reign<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2'>1Ki 2</a><br/> Builds the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5'>1Ki 5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=10'>1Ki 9:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=10'>1Ch 6:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2'>2Ch 2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=7&verse=11'>2Ch 7:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=20'>Jer 52:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=47'>Act 7:47</a><br/> Dedicates the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8'>1Ki 8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=6'>2Ch 6</a><br/> Renews the courses of the priests and Levites, and the forms of service according to the commandment of Moses and the regulations of David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=16'>2Ch 8:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=4'>2Ch 35:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=45'>Neh 12:45</a><br/> Builds his palace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=1'>1Ki 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=1'>1Ki 7:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=8'>1Ki 7:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=10'>1Ki 9:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=7&verse=11'>2Ch 7:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=1'>2Ch 8:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=2&verse=4'>Ecc 2:4</a><br/> Builds his house of the forest of Lebanon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=7'>1Ki 7:7</a><br/> Builds for Pharaoh's daughter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=12'>1Ki 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=24'>1Ki 9:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=11'>2Ch 8:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=2&verse=4'>Ecc 2:4</a><br/> Ivory throne of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=7'>1Ki 7:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=20'>1Ki 10:20</a><br/> Porches of judgment<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=7'>1Ki 7:7</a><br/> Builds Millo, the wall of Jerusalem, the cities of Hazor, Megiddo, Gezer, Beth-Horon, Baalath, Tadmor, store cities, and cities for chariots, and for cavalry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=19'>1Ki 9:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=25'>2Ch 9:25</a><br/> Provides an armory<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=17'>1Ki 10:17</a><br/> Plants vineyards and orchards of all kinds of fruit trees; makes pools<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=2&verse=6'>Ecc 2:6</a><br/> Imports apes and peacocks<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=22'>1Ki 10:22</a><br/> Drinking vessels of his houses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=21'>1Ki 10:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=20'>2Ch 9:20</a><br/> Musicians and musical instruments of his court<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=12'>1Ki 10:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=11'>2Ch 9:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=2&verse=8'>Ecc 2:8</a><br/> The splendor of his court<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=9'>1Ki 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=12'>1Ki 10:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=8'>2Ch 9:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=2&verse=9'>Ecc 2:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=29'>Mat 6:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=27'>Luk 12:27</a><br/> Commerce of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=28'>1Ki 9:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=12'>1Ki 10:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=22'>1Ki 10:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=29'>1Ki 10:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=1&verse=17'>2Ch 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=18'>2Ch 8:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=22'>2Ch 9:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=28'>2Ch 9:28</a><br/> Presents received by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=10'>1Ki 10:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=9'>2Ch 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=24'>2Ch 9:24</a><br/> Is visited by the queen of Sheba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=13'>1Ki 10:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=12'>2Ch 9:12</a><br/> Wealth of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9'>1Ki 9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=10'>1Ki 10:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=15'>1Ki 10:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=23'>1Ki 10:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=27'>1Ki 10:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=1&verse=15'>2Ch 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=1'>2Ch 9:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=9'>2Ch 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=13'>2Ch 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=24'>2Ch 9:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=27'>2Ch 9:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=1&verse=16'>Ecc 1:16</a><br/> Has seven hundred wives and three hundred concubines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=3'>1Ki 11:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=17'>Deu 17:17</a><br/> Their influence over him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=4'>1Ki 11:4</a><br/> Marries one of Pharaoh's daughters<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=1'>1Ki 3:1</a><br/> Builds idolatrous temples<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=8'>1Ki 11:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=13'>2Ki 23:13</a><br/> His idolatry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=4'>1Ki 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=13'>2Ki 23:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=26'>Neh 13:26</a><br/> Extent of his dominions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=21'>1Ki 4:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=24'>1Ki 4:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=65'>1Ki 8:65</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=7&verse=8'>2Ch 7:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=26'>2Ch 9:26</a><br/> Receives tribute<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=21'>1Ki 4:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=21'>1Ki 9:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=8'>2Ch 8:8</a><br/> Officers of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=35'>1Ki 2:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=19'>1Ki 4:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=10'>2Ch 8:10</a><br/> His purveyors<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=19'>1Ki 4:19</a><br/> Divides his kingdom into subsistence departments; the daily subsistence rate for his court<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=23'>1Ki 4:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=28'>1Ki 4:28</a><br/> Military equipment of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=26'>1Ki 4:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=28'>1Ki 4:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=17'>1Ki 10:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=26'>1Ki 10:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=28'>1Ki 10:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=1&verse=14'>2Ch 1:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=25'>2Ch 9:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=16'>Deu 17:16</a><br/> Cedes certain cities to Hiram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=13'>1Ki 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=2'>2Ch 8:2</a><br/> Wisdom and fame of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=34'>1Ki 4:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=4'>1Ki 10:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=8'>1Ki 10:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=24'>1Ki 10:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=25'>1Ch 29:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=7'>2Ch 9:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=23'>2Ch 9:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=1&verse=16'>Ecc 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=42'>Mat 12:42</a><br/> Piety of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=15'>1Ki 3:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=29'>1Ki 4:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8'>1Ki 8</a><br/> Beloved of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=24'>2Sa 12:24</a><br/> Justice of, illustrated in his judgment of the two harlots<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=28'>1Ki 3:28</a><br/> Oppressions of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=4'>1Ki 12:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=10&verse=4'>2Ch 10:4</a><br/> Reigns forty years<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=30'>2Ch 9:30</a><br/> Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=31'>2Ch 9:31</a><br/> Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=7&verse=16'>2Sa 7:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=13'>1Ki 11:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=17&verse=14'>1Ch 17:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=28&verse=7'>1Ch 28:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=132&verse=11'>Psa 132:11</a><br/> A type of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=45&verse=17'>Psa 45:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=72'>Psa 72</a>"}]}